discovery_rule.name: SAA Discovery
discovery_rule.description: Discovery of rttMonCtrlAdminTable, a table of SAA pool monitoring entries.

item_prototype.name: {#SAA_OWNER}: Monitor admin frequency
item_prototype.description: Specifies the duration between initiating each RTT operation.

item_prototype.name: {#SAA_OWNER}: Monitor admin status
item_prototype.description: The status of the conceptual RTT control row.

item_prototype.name: {#SAA_OWNER}: Monitor admin threshold
item_prototype.description: The type of RTT operation to be performed. This value must be set in the same PDU or before setting any type specific configuration.

item_prototype.name: {#SAA_OWNER}: Monitor admin timeout
item_prototype.description: Specifies the duration to wait for a RTT operation completion. The value of this object cannot be set to a value which would specify a duration exceeding rttMonCtrlAdminFrequency.

item_prototype.name: {#SAA_OWNER}: Monitor Type
item_prototype.description: The type of RTT operation to be performed. This value must be set in the same PDU or before setting any type specific configuration.

item_prototype.name: {#SAA_OWNER}: Monitor Jitter Packet Loss D -> S
